            <description><![CDATA[【🍂秋天可能会把你“送”进精神科？真的！】秋冬季节更容易emo真不是你的错觉<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[失望]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shiwang-b4bf17068f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>，从心理学的角度看，秋冬季节气温下降，光照减少，容易引起生理节律紊乱和内分泌失调，严重者甚至会发展为“季节性情感障碍”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[伤心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_shangxin-49b2fe44a6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>不管你是谁，身在哪，经历过什么，卫都希望你天天开心<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_xin-43af9086c0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[笑哈哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/lxh/lxh_xiaohaha-56dbc288a5.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>（反正小卫身在岭南，短袖不知秋<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj2snrmxy6j20u0334tl0.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj2sns6hbdj20u034qnar.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj2snrpnpsj20u03yyqm3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
